sources.title: Fatal Call | Full Movie | Action Thriller | Kevin Sorbo | Danielle Harris
sources.description:
Fatal Call - Starting a new life in the big city, Mitch meets Amy while out with co-workers. Amy, a woman out of his league, draws him into an exciting romance. Soon, Mitch finds himself accused of murder and on the run, relentlessly pursued by both the law and an unknown killer. Confronted by both his past and his present, Mitch must find an ultimate solution before time runs out!
2012.  Stars: Jason London, Danielle Harris, Kevin Sorbo

sources.description:
Fatal Call - Leaving his small-town roots to start a new life, Mitch meets the beautiful and seductive Amy at a happy hour and begins a tantalizing romance. Before long, Mitch learns that nothing is as it appears and, unable to trust anyone, finds himself on a nightmarish roller coaster ride, accused of murder and running from the law and a mysterious stranger out to kill him. Surviving by quick thinking and his wits, Mitch must confront both his past and present and find a solution before time runs out!
2012.  Stars: Jason London, Danielle Harris, Kevin Sorbo
